lead_paragraph: Red Bull's Daniil Kvyat apologised to Ferrari's Sebastian Vettel, and braced for criticism, after crashing into the German in a moment of May Day madness at his home Russian Grand Prix on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Kvyat and Red Bull Apologise to Vettel for Crash
headline.main: Kvyat and Red Bull Apologise to Vettel for Crash
